 to the treacherous desert, each area offers new dangers and opportunities for mayhem.\n\nCandy-packed Enemies: These pi\u00f1atas are somehow thinking, moving, and growing smarter!\n\nHidden Secrets: Find the hidden Ninjas in every level by looking high and low.", "short_description": "EXPERIENCE THE DEMO FOR ROGUE PINATAS: VRMAGEDDON!\n\nA multiplayer VR roguelite game. Your mission? Survive the party-apocalyptic world by bashing your way through swarms of invading Pi\u00f1atas, where every swing could mean survival or sweet defeat!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://nerdninjas.com/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Nerd Ninjas", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://nerdninjas.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "644354873106712"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "8155850074523275"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1084496399689043"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1084496399689043"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1728914520, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1084496399689043"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8229566277151654", "version": "0.1.0"}, "id": "1517859325512561", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_onl